snippet.title: Mecha Force - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Watch the trailer for Mecha Force to learn about the story and, of course, get a look at a massive mech. A demo for Mecha Force is available now on the Meta Quest App Lab.

#SummerOfGaming
